did.head: DESCRIPTIVE SUMMARY
did.physdesc: Correspondence, minutes, financial records, photographs and mimeographs.
did.repository: Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library
did.abstract: Personal correspondence; correspondence, minutes, and bills relating to the University Senate and Constituent Assembly and the University Faculty; mimeographed Faculty and Senate records; and Board of Trustees correspondence and mimeographs; also professional correspondence and work, and photographs.

scopecontent.head: COLLECTION DESCRIPTION
scopecontent.p: Personal correspondence; correspondence, minutes, and bills relating to the University Senate and Constituent Assembly and the University Faculty; mimeographed Faculty and Senate records; and Board of Trustees correspondence and mimeographs; also professional correspondence and work, and photographs.
